  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Take over the city at extreme velocity!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop on your sci-fi motorcycle and complete various races, time trials and other challenges in a neon lit metropolis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/cda174904597a4bfff5c1bcf9ad300ec.poster.avif?t=1739889326\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/cda174904597a4bfff5c1bcf9ad300ec.webm?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/cda174904597a4bfff5c1bcf9ad300ec.mp4?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyber-bikes with future tech</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack, boost and maneuver with different futuristic bikes on the endless highway. Tune up your vehicle with system updates and hardware upgrades - be the fastest racer in a world dominated by adrenaline seeking speedsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drive like a cyber-maniac!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your racing skills and reflexes, dodge the police and knock out enemy motorbikes, while you zig-zag between futuristic traffic. Get higher speed and exact handling, use boosts and hacking tactically to leave your foes behind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the best trial time of other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/ddb5e6075b66b9c29b20d8067829f039.poster.avif?t=1739889326\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/ddb5e6075b66b9c29b20d8067829f039.webm?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/ddb5e6075b66b9c29b20d8067829f039.mp4?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go hard!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the glowing, futuristic streets, find every boost, unlock every vehicle, beat every boss and collect as many coins as you can to upgrade your vehicle reaching extreme high speeds! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >32 SECS will take you on a unique futuristic high-speed experience. Rush and take chances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck rider!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Take over the city at extreme velocity!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop on your sci-fi motorcycle and complete various races, time trials and other challenges in a neon lit metropolis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/cda174904597a4bfff5c1bcf9ad300ec.poster.avif?t=1739889326\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/cda174904597a4bfff5c1bcf9ad300ec.webm?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/cda174904597a4bfff5c1bcf9ad300ec.mp4?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyber-bikes with future tech</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack, boost and maneuver with different futuristic bikes on the endless highway. Tune up your vehicle with system updates and hardware upgrades - be the fastest racer in a world dominated by adrenaline seeking speedsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drive like a cyber-maniac!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your racing skills and reflexes, dodge the police and knock out enemy motorbikes, while you zig-zag between futuristic traffic. Get higher speed and exact handling, use boosts and hacking tactically to leave your foes behind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the best trial time of other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/ddb5e6075b66b9c29b20d8067829f039.poster.avif?t=1739889326\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/ddb5e6075b66b9c29b20d8067829f039.webm?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390250/extras/ddb5e6075b66b9c29b20d8067829f039.mp4?t=1739889326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go hard!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the glowing, futuristic streets, find every boost, unlock every vehicle, beat every boss and collect as many coins as you can to upgrade your vehicle reaching extreme high speeds! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >32 SECS will take you on a unique futuristic high-speed experience. Rush and take chances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck rider!</p>",
